title: Platin Support sucht skilled adc!

embed.description: Summoner Lookup with statistics, ratings, LoLSkillScore and more for MadlifeThrash, a League of Legends summoner on the Europe West region.

body:
Platin 4 Support, letzte season Platin 1 sucht mal wieder einen Adc der was kann.
